    "The identical filtering ensures that any downstream performance differences can be attributed solely to extraction quality rather than filtering strategies.",
    "Pretraining SetupTraining.",
    "The models utilized in this work are 1.5B parameter decoder-only transformers derived from the Qwen3 model family.",
    "For the standard pretraining configuration, each model is trained from scratch on a selected subset of 62B tokens.",
    "A comprehensive description of the architecture and training setup is available in Appendix C.Evaluation Benchmarks."
